27
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,550
Yesterday, His Majesty ordered him flogging

28
00:01:50,780 --> 00:01:51,890
before granting him an audience.

29
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:57,870
Has a physician seen him?
Did he get any medicine?

30
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:00,080
He is all right,

31
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,550
but he worries about you.

32
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:03,830
He told me not to let you know.

33
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,290
Best if you act like you never heard.

34
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:19,720
I understand.

35
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:21,960
Thank you.

36
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,790
Though punished,

37
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,830
he drew the Imperial Guards' attention.

38
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,870
The case files on Qiao Ping and Begonia Snow

39
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:28,780
have been submitted.

40
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,710
Things might change soon.

41
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,790
Please wait here patiently.

42
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:36,960
Miss Jiang.

43
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,590
I'll take my leave now.

44
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:48,710
Even when things are tough for you,

45
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:52,310
you still risk yourself for me.

46
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:56,910
Xiao Jingchu,

47
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,510
am I really worth it?

48
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:29,760
Leyao.

49
00:03:29,890 --> 00:03:30,740
Leyao.

50
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:31,620
Xiao Jingchu.

51
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,640
It's alright, let's go.

52
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,680
I'll get you out of here.

53
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,080
Did you see that?

54
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:41,440
The one you love

55
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:43,870
will be lost in the flames.

56
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,040
Xiao Jingchu!

57
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:54,070
Don't move, you have a fever.

58
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,830
Xiao Jingchu...

59
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:09,670
What's going on here?

60
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,840
Did you miss me?

61
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:15,800
Mm.

62
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:20,230
I've missed you. Truly missed you.

63
00:04:21,620 --> 00:04:24,560
♪Wine is quick to intoxicate,
and cups to break♪

64
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:26,380
♪Pour a cup, drink it up♪

65
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:27,430
(Xiao Jingchu,)

66
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:31,190
(I swear, I won't let you die.)

67
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:34,030
Don't worry, I'm right here.

68
00:04:35,730 --> 00:04:38,880
♪Drunken whispers fade,
and I fall asleep♪

69
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,160
He is alright,

70
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,350
but he worries about you.

71
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,390
He told me not to let you know.

72
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:45,790
Best if you act like you never heard.

73
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,460
You may leave now.

74
