(Double Happiness)

75
00:05:52,060 --> 00:05:53,090
Have you forgotten

76
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,200
you're already gone?

77
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,950
Xuanyin Division's warrant is out now.

78
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,590
But rest assured, My Lady.

79
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,430
I promise I won't trouble you.

80
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,200
Is that so?

81
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:13,040
So what will you do now?

82
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,950
Xiao Jingchu won't let go

83
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,510
the one he seeks,

84
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:22,070
unless that person dead.

85
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,550
My life belongs to you, My Lady.

86
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:36,710
Then use your life

87
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:40,190
to help me one last time.

88
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:45,510
As for whether you'll survive,

89
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:50,790
that depends on your fate.

90
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,310
I've come to bid you farewell.

91
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,280
Before I leave,

92
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,750
I'll deal with that wealthy merchant.

93
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:07,230
My Lady, please take care.

94
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:11,680
You may go now.

95
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,390
Will the Crown Prince treat you well?

96
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,880
He will.

97
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:23,310
Will he treat you better than I did?

98
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:26,480
Let go of...

99
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,550
Will he be like me,

100
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:42,670
ready to give his life for you?

101
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,320
They're here.

102
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,670
Jiang Leyao, receive the decree.

103
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:44,350
By the Mandate of Heaven,
the Emperor decrees,

104
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,790
the case of Jiang Leyao

105
00:08:47,160 --> 00:08:49,390
involves the life of Guard Qiao Ping.

106
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,390
After thorough investigation,

107
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:54,190
the evidence for Qiao Ping's death is solid.

108
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:57,430
Such deeds cannot be tolerated by law.

109
00:08:58,000 --> 00:09:01,230
Dali Court shall take over at once.

110
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:03,270
No delay will be allowed.

111
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,470
Thus is the imperial command.

112
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,280
Guards.

113
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,430
Take Jiang Leyao

114
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:17,350
to the Meridian Gate for execution.

115
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:19,190
Let's see who dares touch her.

116
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:21,030
(I'm wondering)

117
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:23,030
(how Ning Bingqing's wedding is going.)

118
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,510
I'm angry, yes,

119
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:30,950
but I did watch her grow up.

120
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:34,110
That day when Jingchu came to see me.

121
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,470
That reminded me

122
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,430
her wedding with the Crown Prince

123
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:41,310
was indeed held in haste.

124
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:44,870
