126
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:48,670
in the Crown Prince's manor.

127
00:09:49,620 --> 00:09:53,430
You're kind, Your Majesty,
and Jingchu is thoughtful.

128
00:09:58,190 --> 00:09:59,030
This...

129
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:01,950
